{"tid":1535084,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張飛: 機場=春袋 大橋=鳩筋","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T00:00:40.000Z","uid":74778,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ba854ba16ff5970d4981bf62e4bdcb541e81e5","tid":1535084,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"軍事上有一個名詞叫作choke point， 中文可譯為咽喉位。例如，霍爾木茲海峽就是全球石油供應的choke point，因為波斯灣啟航的運油輪全經此海峽，其闊度最窄只有39km。 伊朗經常威脅出兵霍爾木茲海峽對抗美國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69b8b9b8fdc00f2a4ad816e931c6dde76255ffc","tid":1535084,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53843b48709ec5efd3daf648f0b0f73e53b0a073","tid":1535084,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:28:18.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"956de1e383b2360c731a3781ba77675fe93