b5abf105712ae63","tid":1535084,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"齊齊合法遊車河"},{"pid":"a00fb8a8df22049d90334f33f2ec4fd334cd99b9","tid":1535084,"uid":120760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"其實香港最危險地方係邊？<br />\n係青衣油庫<br />\n咁近青馬大橋<br />\n一有任何事都會影響青馬大橋的出入<br />\n<br />\n就算唔講青衣油庫(油庫既管理都好嚴，發生爆炸等危險情況好低)<br />\n剩係青馬大橋同相連的汲水門大橋都死啦<br />\n睇下呢單2015年10月23日汲水門大橋封閉事件：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2015%E5%B9%B410%E6%9C%8823%E6%97%A5%E6%B1%B2%E6%B0%B4%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E5%B0%81%E9%96%89%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2015%25E5%25B9%25B410%25E6%259C%258823%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25B1%25B2%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2596%2589%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=ee21550f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2015%E5%B9%B410%E6%9C%8823%E6%97%A5%E6%B1%B2%E6%B0%B4%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E5%B0%81%E9%96%89%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n政府到底有無真係保證無任何問題？"},{"pid":"de75b76d0b3e5bdd73c1dc2cfa35da60cd41ad13","tid":1535084,"uid":154579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:03:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1531743/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1531743/page/1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57ef30aa7b45304e36736bf0f729d1ec1db62d2","tid":1535084,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3ba854ba16ff5970d4981bf62e4bdcb541e81e5","tid":1535084,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"軍事上有一個名詞叫作choke point， 中文可譯為咽喉位。例如，霍爾木茲海峽就是全球石油供應的choke point，因為波斯灣啟航的運油輪全經此海峽，其闊度最窄只有39km。 伊朗經常威脅出兵霍爾木茲海峽對抗美國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"放東涌比人接送，即係空管主任同crew都番到工<br />\n航班唔會delay/cancel"},{"pid":"40ca2453793e7353c31ec680f1f74a7deb59f649","tid":1535084,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"最後你地咪又係怕死 付出少少都唔敢<br />\n諗埋啲度縮方法"},{"pid":"582334c88a6a0063915d36ba6c3b25c10bbfd23e","tid":1535084,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"}]}